<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tax Organizer For 2025</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; padding: 20px;"
  >
    <table
      style="max-width:600px; width:100%; margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
          <h2 style="color: #2a7ae2;">Hi {{name}},</h2>

          <h3>2026 is here and its time to get ready to file 2025.</h3>
          <p>We’re reaching out to help you get organized and ready to file
            2025. Please review the attached tax organizer—it will guide you
            through the documents you may need and help make the process simple
            and stress-free.</p>
          <p>We’ll be looking for things like:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>W-2s and 1099s</li>
            <li>Recent pay stubs or proof of income</li>
            <li>Records of any estimated payments</li>
            <li>Deductions (mortgage interest, charitable donations, medical
              expenses, etc.)</li>
            <li>Dependent information and filing preferences</li>
          </ul>
          <p>This is about making your filing accurate, complete, and on time.
            So if you have any questions or concerns don't hesitate to call us,
            we are here to help.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Call our consultant
            help line at
            <a
              href="tel:+13105796719"
              style="color: #2a7ae2; text-decoration: none;"
            > 310-579-6719</a>
            if you have any questions, and we’ll go over it together.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            {{{signature}}}
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>